# Phrases Content Map

Common expressions organised by communicative function.

## Route Structure

```
/learn/phrases/:tab
```

Tabs: survival, responses, requests, opinions, connectors, time

Note: "patterns" tab (μου αρέσει, με λένε) has moved to /reference/patterns

## Data Source

DB queries via `getPhrasesData()` in `data.server.ts`:
- `getVocabBySection("phrases")` - Main phrase content
- `getVocabBySection("reference")` - Days, months
- `getVocabBySection("verbs")` - Likes construction

